tags: [[Running Conversion]]
title: Output Panels
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A successful Convert populates four state areas the Console renders:

|!Output                    |!Where stored                                |
|Staged tiddlers            |`$:/temp/json-convert/staged/<index>`        |
|Errors                     |`$:/state/json-convert/result/errors`        |
|Warnings                   |`$:/state/json-convert/result/warnings`      |
|Existing-title collisions  |`$:/state/json-convert/result/collisions`    |

The staging table renders the staged tiddlers, with collisions surfaced as their own section (see [[Conflicts vs New]]).  Errors and warnings show in dedicated panels above.
